data.description: Adorable bungalow in the Linley Park area. Also, walking distance to neighborhood bench swing and gazebo just for relaxing. Meticulously maintained. Per seller, since ownership, new plumbing has been done 2004, heat system 2015, house roof 2017, garage metal roof 2004, new gas water heater & hut 2021, garbage disposal 2018, windows 2003, both back fiberglass exterior doors at sunroom installed 2007. Seller has also had sewer lines to street replaced 2004. The house had just been treated in/out by exterminator 10/2023. See complete list attached.  Really cute touches, just needs someone like you to make it your own. Eat-in kitchen with access to sunroom. Flex room currently used as den, can also use as formal dining room or 3rd bedroom. Back door to driveway and oversized one car detached garage. Behind the garage is a shed with electricity and private backyard. A convenient location to hospital, shopping our quaint downtown Anderson, and the desirable area of Linley Park with walking trail, ball park, playground and picnic area to enjoy with your friends or family. Don't let this one get away.
